description:
READY? SET? GO KART!

Do you enjoy the wind blowing in your open roof car? Do you want to speed down an empty highway? Do you dream of being in NASCAR? Well this App is for you! Player will dodge, jump and weave through endless torrents of orange cones, road blocks and banana peels.    Experience a whole new level of driving with our NEWELY DEVELOPED Swipe-drive to control your vehicle.  No need for buttons or arrows to block your gaming screen but control, left, right and jump, all with a swipe of your finger.  Let your fingers do all the magic! The great thing about Super Go Kart is all the different places that you’ll be able to race, from the scorching deserts of Egypt to the beautiful cherry blossom fields of Japan.    

How long can you survive?  

 Come and drive SUPER GO KART!
releaseNotes:
Check out the updated Super Go Kart! 
Here's what's new: 

- Test your skills in the new exciting City environment! 

- Race through levels with new challenging obstacles!

- Use boosts to achieve high scores and earn FREE stars!

- Graphics improvements and bug fixes.

If you like Super GoKart, be sure to try our new game 
Wild Runner Adventure! Available now in the App Store.
 

Your feedback is important to us so if you enjoy the update, rate us 5 stars in iTunes and we will continue to bring you fun mobile games and exciting events on Fantage!
